7.3. Form Fields & Inputs
Inputs / Textareas:

Border 1 px var(--color-divider), border-radius 4 px, padding 12 px all around.

Focus: outline none; border color var(--color-primary-blue), box-shadow 0 0 0 2 px rgba(18, 100, 163, 0.2).

Placeholder color var(--text-tertiary) (#A3A2A3).

7.4. Cards & Panels
